      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this wonderful vehicle! It is in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a reliable and smooth driving experience. While it shows some light, standard wear from regular use, it remains a fantastic choice for anyone looking for a dependable and attractive car. This is a solid, honest vehicle that's ready for many more miles of memories!",
