    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a major restoration project or a reliable source of spare parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including several areas of rust and faded paint, while the interior requires a complete overhaul. Mechanically, the engine requires substantial work to be roadworthy again, and the transmission is showing signs of failure. We recommend towing the vehicle from the lot, as it is not currently in a condition for daily driving.",
