    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to a standard that exceeds even the most discerning expectations. This specimen remains in showroom condition, featuring an unblemished exterior and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance and long-term reliability. For the individual who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
